🐠🌿A beautiful calm Freshwater Pond along Diversity Trail.
🍃🦐🍂The quiet embience, void of people and traffic noise, adds a serenity to the entire surrounding.
🐢🐟🐝Freshwater Ponds are aquatic environment that support a diverse ecosystem including aquatic life and other wildlife.
🐟🌿Enjoy the tranquil Pond enroute Diversity Trail.
